API endpoints:

GET /game/config - returns something similar to config.js
GET /game/statistics
GET /game/translations/:language
GET /game/top/:amount - top x players

GET /player - info about the currently logged in player, technologies researched
GET /player/events
POST /player/tech/upgrade - upgrade technologies
GET /player/:id/profile

GET /planet/:id - building levels, resources, fleet
POST /planet/:id/build - build buildings, fleet, defense and so on
GET /planet/:id/fleet
POST /planet/:id/fleet/send
GET /planet/:id/events

GET /galaxy/:id/:solar_system - planet listing
POST /search

[alliance]

GET /player/messages
POST /player/messages/send
GET /player/messages/thread/:id